com.google.crypto.tink.subtle

Interface EngineWrapper<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EngineWrapper.TCipher, EngineWrapper.TKeyAgreement, EngineWrapper.TKeyFactory, EngineWrapper.TKeyPairGenerator, EngineWrapper.TMac, EngineWrapper.TMessageDigest, EngineWrapper.TSignature

    public interface EngineWrapper<T>
    Interface and its implentations to make JCE Engines have a common parent.

    There's no expected reason to directly import this for users of Tink, but it might be needed to implement it (say, if someone wants a new type of engine).

    Since:
    1.0.0
